author: Retro Game Corps
description:
In preparation of my Odin 3 review video, I tested over 110 games to get a state of the Snapdragon 8 Elite's performance with stock drives on a dedicated handheld.  Here are the results!

Buy the Odin 3 here: https://tinyurl.com/RGC-Odin3
